                <h1></h1>
                <p>A BGC (Background Check) is a comprehensive examination of a person's history, typically conducted by employers or organizations. It includes checking criminal records, employment history, credit ratings, and other relevant data. This process helps ensure safety and trustworthiness in hiring decisions, safeguarding both the company and its clients.</p>
